{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/dilan-1991-pecahkan-rekor-box-office-indonesia-kalahkan-infinity-war/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Kalahkan Infinity War, Dilan 1991 Pecahkan Rekor Box Office Indonesia","content":"\n<p>Thanos berhasil menyapu bersih separuh makhluk hidup di\njagat raya. Satu-satunya orang yang bisa menghentikannya adalah… Dilan?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Avengers: Infinity War boleh saja menjadi salah satu event monumental dalam dunia perfilman dan pop culture. Namun setidaknya di Indonesia, kumpulan superhero terhebat Marvel tersebut masih kalah melawan pasangan kekasih Dilan dan Milea dari film Dilan 1991. Tak hanya mengalahkan rekor Infinity War, film ini juga memecahkan rekor box office Indonesia!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53227\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dilan-1991-pecahkan-rekor-box-office-indonesia-kalahkan-infinity-war/attachment/01-dilan-1991-rekor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-dilan-1991-rekor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-dilan-1991-rekor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Terkini\" class=\"wp-image-53227\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-dilan-1991-rekor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Terkini</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Dilansir dari Viva, film Dilan 1991 berhasil menjaring 800\nribu penonton dalan rentang waktu premiere (24 Februari) hingga tayang perdanan\n(28 Februari). Bahkan di hari ketiga, film sekuel dari Dilan 1990 ini berhasil\nmenjaring lebih dari 2 juta penonton! Ini adalah rekor box office tertinggi di\nIndonesia untuk penayangan hari pertama.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>“Terima kasih apresiasinya penonton Indonesia, mari dukung\nterus film dalam negeri dan menjadi yang terbaik di negeri sendiri,” ungkap\npihak Max Pictures selaku studio produksi film Dilan 1991 dalam sebuah rilis.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53228\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dilan-1991-pecahkan-rekor-box-office-indonesia-kalahkan-infinity-war/attachment/02-dilan-1991-rekor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-dilan-1991-rekor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-dilan-1991-rekor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Astro Gempak\" class=\"wp-image-53228\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-dilan-1991-rekor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Astro Gempak</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Hal ini pun didukung oleh data yang dirilis oleh situs internasional <a href=\"https://deadline.com/2019/03/how-to-train-your-dragon-the-hidden-world-green-book-alita-battle-angel-dilan-1991-china-global-international-box-office-1202568434/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Deadline</a>. Dilan 1991 berhasil meraup keuntungan sebesar $2.05 juta US Dollar (sekitar Rp. 28.2 miliar) di hari pertama penayangan. Jumlah ini mengalahkan Avengers: Infinity War yang mencapai $1.79 juta US Dollar (sekitar Rp.25.3 miliar) di hari pertama.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pencapaian hari pertama film Dilan 1991 ini pun mendapat\napresiasi dari Museum Rekor Indonesia. &#8220;Hari ini saya bangga karena bisa\nhadir di satu peristiwa bersejarah. Semoga yang terjadi hari ini bisa\nmenyemangati film Indonesia menaklukkan film dunia,” ujar Jaya Suprana selaku\npendiri MURI, dalam acara penyerahan plakat MURI di XXI Kota Kasablanka tanggal\n3 Maret lalu.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53229\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dilan-1991-pecahkan-rekor-box-office-indonesia-kalahkan-infinity-war/attachment/03-dilan-1991-rekor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-dilan-1991-rekor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-dilan-1991-rekor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg\" alt=\"dilan 1991\" class=\"wp-image-53229\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-dilan-1991-rekor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Duniaku</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;Terima kasih sudah diberi rekor (MURI),” balas produser Dilan 1991 Ody Mulya Hidayat. “Saya senang bisa kalahin film Avengers. Semoga film lokal bisa merajai negara sendiri.” Ody kemudian menargetkan film tersebut bisa mengalahkan rekor jumlah penonton dari film Warkop DKI Reborn Part 1, sebanyak 6.8 juta penonton. Target Ody itu pun langsung diamini oleh Jaya Suprana.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dilan 1991 melanjutkan kisah dari film Dilan 1990. Milea\n(Vanesa Priscilla) kini sudah berpacaran dengan Dilan (Iqbaal Ramadhan), namun\nkini ia harus berusaha menerima kehidupan lain Dilan sebagai panglima geng\nmotor. Selain itu, kehadiran berbagai tokoh baru dalam film ini akan menguji\nkesetiaan Milea kepada Dilan sang peramal dan pujangga.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53230\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dilan-1991-pecahkan-rekor-box-office-indonesia-kalahkan-infinity-war/attachment/04-dilan-1991-rekor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-dilan-1991-rekor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-dilan-1991-rekor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Alinea\" class=\"wp-image-53230\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-dilan-1991-rekor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-dilan-1991-rekor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Alinea</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Nah, apakah film Dilan 1991 mampu menciptakan rekor baru dan sejarah baru dalam dunia perfilman Indonesia? Dilan 1991, diadaptasi dari novel karangan Pidi Baiq, sudah bisa kamu saksikan di bioskop terdekat. Jangan lupa pula buat baca <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"komik Dilan 1990 (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/komik-dilan-1990-ciayo-comics/\" target=\"_blank\">komik Dilan 1990</a> di CIAYO Comics, dan mainkan <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-games-dan-agate-luncurkan-game-dilan-official/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"game Dilan official (opens in a new tab)\">game Dilan official</a> di CIAYO Stories!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"32122e68-279e-54b9-890e-a8f03f1bb0b1"}}}